Body: Description: I am hoping to upgrade our current console V11.5 to 11.6. The hope of this ticket was to schedule the initial call to back up our tool and prepare for the upgrade.

+++++
1) Successfully upgraded to NEA v 11.6.0.141
2) Could not upgrade to AIC 11.6.0.37 because we did not have the password for the Windows Account = "StealthID"
3) Could not get NEA Reporting Module working because we did not have an SSL CERT  assigned to/for the NEA Application server.  (certmgr)
